snippet.title: Amunet - Bloody Hunt (Character Trailer) | Dislyte
snippet.description:
Zora is no longer willing to question whether her divine power is a gift, or a curse.
For the hunters of Graywater, emotions are superfluous.
The confusion, pain, and hatred she once felt, all have turned into sharp blades in her hands – cutting through the sinners among the shadows.
